Package net.sourceforge.wurfl.core.resource

Includes the wurfl resources file loaders and transformers.

          Description

Interface Summary
WURFLModel This interface is used to access to the ModelDevices.
WURFLResource This interface represents a WURFL resource as the WURFL main file and a WURFL patch file.
 

Class Summary
DefaultWURFLModel This is the default WURFLModel implementation.
ModelDevice This immutable class represent a device defined in WURFL repository.
ModelDevice.Builder Builder used to build ModelDevice instance.
ModelDevices A Collection of ModelDevice.
ModelDeviceWithAncestorId Date: 12/06/11 Runtime info to build a device with low performance impact.
WURFLResources Collection of WURFLResource.
XmlFileLoader Parser for WURFL resources.
XMLResource XMLResource
